metadata.name: Fallen Sacrifices
metadata.description:
The first of the series, the first event on this journey

"an anointed man loses everything,
his hope, his love and his sanity,
all in an attempt to awaken a new light.

under the last rains, under the red sun, away from the strange man, the birds run free

A man who craved light and a woman born with it, surely the world can bear the demise; a woman born of the earth becomes a fallen sacrifice

And as the clouds keep weeping,
he is left broken,
as though,
nature never forgave him."
